[SPEAKER_06]: Is there a motion?

633
01:09:57,249 --> 01:10:00,969
[SPEAKER_06]: Motion to approve.

634
01:10:01,009 --> 01:10:03,710
[SPEAKER_06]: A motion to approve the resolution by Councilor Tseng, seconded by?

635
01:10:04,750 --> 01:10:06,111
[SPEAKER_06]: Seconded by Councilor Callahan.

