[SPEAKER_17]: Councilor Scarpelli?

644
01:10:17,119 --> 01:10:17,260
[SPEAKER_17]: No.

645
01:10:18,360 --> 01:10:19,081
[SPEAKER_17]: Councilor Tseng?

646
01:10:19,101 --> 01:10:20,302
[SPEAKER_17]: Yes.

647
01:10:20,322 --> 01:10:21,483
[SPEAKER_17]: Vice President Lazzaro?

648
