[SPEAKER_17]: Yes.

649
01:10:23,905 --> 01:10:24,545
[SPEAKER_17]: President Pierce?

650
01:10:24,825 --> 01:10:25,065
[SPEAKER_06]: Yes.

651
01:10:25,466 --> 01:10:26,627
[SPEAKER_06]: Six in the affirmative, one in the negative.

652
01:10:26,647 --> 01:10:27,407
[SPEAKER_06]: The motion passes.

653
01:10:32,291 --> 01:10:33,332
[SPEAKER_06]: Any further discussion?

654
